Bug 1866822 - Reshuffle MIME tree for PGP/MIME to avoid multipart/mixed layer.

This works in principle but parsing the tree from the decrypted data and
re-assembling it leads to small differences which make the signature invalid.

So the processing in MimeTree.sys.mjs needs to be left untouched and the multipart/mixed layer
needs to removed in mimeDecrypt.sys.mjs.

